msgid "Allows to change the runtime behaviour of liquids"
msgstr "Likidoen portaera unean bertan aldatzea ahalbidetzen du"

msgid "This command is used to debug liquid transformation"
msgstr "Komando hau likidoen transformazioa arazteko da"

msgid "This command sets the time passed between Luanti ticks."
msgstr "Komando honekin Luantiko tick-en arteko denbora aldatzen da."

msgid "If this value is larger than the actual tick, liquids become faster than specified."
msgstr "Uneko tick-a baino balio handiagoa badu, likidoak espero baino azkarragoan izango dira."

